    "Furthermore, movies are compressed using three different compression rates: the original (c0), the significantly compressed (c23), and the low-quality video (c40).",
    "Also, C23 movies are near to lossless compression, with a compression quantization value of 23.",
    "Also, c40 movies have a compression quantization value of 40.Faceswapping is used to construct DeepFakeTIMIT, which is based on the VidTIMIT dataset.",
    "Low-quality (LQ) and high-quality (HQ) fake movies are divided into two categories, each with a distinct resolution of fabricated faces.",
